article.description: — Leon Ayers III and Felipe Haase scored 17 points apiece as Mercer topped Georgia State 86-69 on Monday night.
article.headline: Ayers III, Haase lift Mercer past Georgia State 86-69
article.linkText: Ayers III, Haase lift Mercer past Georgia State 86-69
article.story: MACON, Ga. -- — Leon Ayers III and Felipe Haase scored 17 points apiece as Mercer topped Georgia State 86-69 on Monday night. Neftali Alvarez added 16 points and Ross Cummings had 11 points for Mercer (3-0). Alvarez posted eight rebounds and Haase had seven rebounds. Kane Williams had 18 points for the Panthers (2-1). Evan Johnson and Justin Roberts had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
